<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IVertexBuffer.AllocateMemory" Title="AllocateMemory method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IVertexBuffer">IVertexBuffer</PageRef> ->
    AllocateMemory
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>AllocateMemory</TypeRef> method attempts to allocate memory for the buffer using the supplied set of vertex attributes.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[SuccessToken AllocateMemory();]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="SuccessToken">
        True if the operation succeeded, false otherwise. An assertion will be raised in debug builds if the result is not tested.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
